.TH "phy_validate_pause" 9 "phy_validate_pause" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
phy_validate_pause \- Test if the PHY/MAC support the pause configuration
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "bool" phy_validate_pause
.BI "(struct phy_device *phydev "  ","
.BI "struct ethtool_pauseparam *pp "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "phydev" 12
phy_device struct
.IP "pp" 12
requested pause configuration
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Test if the PHY/MAC combination supports the Pause
configuration the user is requesting. Returns True if it is
supported, false otherwise.
